Dagnie goes to confront Dr. Robert Stadler, the brilliant physicist who heads the State Science Institute.

32
00:02:17,819 --> 00:02:22,539
She hopes that this man, once considered one of the greatest scientific minds of the age,

33
00:02:22,539 --> 00:02:27,340
