Stadler admits privately that Reardon Metal is a remarkable thing, but he refuses to say so publicly.

35
00:02:36,539 --> 00:02:40,139
Stadler represents the tragedy of genius without integrity.

36
00:02:40,939 --> 00:02:47,659
Once one of the greatest physicists in the world, he has allowed himself to become

37
