He knows Reardon Medal is safe, but refuses to say so publicly.

58
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:53,339
The intellectual establishments contempt for commerce

59
00:04:53,339 --> 00:04:54,899
is parasitic.

60
00:04:54,899 --> 00:04:58,100
They depend on producers while despising them.

61
00:04:58,100 --> 00:05:02,220
And the attack on Reardon Medal is part of a larger pattern.

62
